{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e436465a47","title":"勇士诛医","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e14e113c4d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":30,"articleId":"e436465a47"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4b20d14954","name":"重庆大学"},{"id":"6254130e31","name":"孙庚武"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4dcd5028ca","type":"title","text":"勇士诛医","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"c452771b4b","type":"authors","text":"重庆大学孙庚武","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"82f685df37","type":"subtitle","text":"[编者按：孙庚武是重庆大学机械系学生。这篇文章是以寓言为形式向党放出的一支冷箭，它污蔑党不敢正视缺点，讳疾忌医，从而贬低反右派斗争的伟大意义。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"8acc596768","type":"subtitle","text":"勇士诛医","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"a91c75d421","type":"paragraph","text":"太古有一勇士，为人人所敬。逢时，勇士当众言之：“闻东山居二虎，恶也！食人畜不分其良善，罪也”！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"4d5d0e6199","type":"paragraph","text":"众闻之，皆大惊！勇士笑而曰：“吾将征东山，灭二虎，尔乐否”？众皆喜。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"620170a17d","type":"paragraph","text":"勇士偶觉不爽，曰之：“群言为真，众见为实，请尔观之，吾是否有不愈之症”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"e9983c6f2f","type":"paragraph","text":"有人曰：“勇士头似东山，拳似北岳，身有长江之伟，气有黄河之巨，焉有病”。勇士闻而大喜，赠以鲜花骏马。一愚医扶杖而前曰：“休矣！吾观之，尔为‘高压症也，应先去西山采药，后奔东山灭虎”！勇士突想挥军杀之，即向众曰：“愚医心怀不测，诛吾人之威，灭吾人之气，愿吾死，即少二虎也”！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"dbb4381c2c","type":"paragraph","text":"次日，勇士借众酣眠之时，直奔西山。其妻问曰：“为何”？勇士向其妻曰：“愚医意恶，该诛！吾之病症该医！故吾明去东山灭虎，暗奔西岳就医，既能为民除害，又能保吾‘尊严’，岂不善也”！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"48083a2af7","type":"paragraph","text":" 6．30","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"d0c4b1e25c","type":"subtitle","text":"过关    孙庚武","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"115e194da6","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：这首诗在资产阶级右派分子的立场上叫嚣“过关是把将来斩，血染刀刃谢苍天”，企图把整风运动引导到资产阶级右派所希冀的方向上去。]","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"3a72825935","type":"paragraph","text":"说过关，道过关，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"4e97a93d3e","type":"paragraph","text":"不知要过那一关？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"e07a11689c","type":"paragraph","text":"山西那里有潼关，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"02756b0475","type":"paragraph","text":"四川还有剑门关，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"1b020813c5","type":"paragraph","text":"关口多的难收尽，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"59ac43f2db","type":"paragraph","text":"每天睡觉把门关！","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"1011d804b1","type":"paragraph","text":"要过关，并不难，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"abf9f23eff","type":"paragraph","text":"望把关口摆面前。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"3236fb7e48","type":"paragraph","text":"不怕雄兵千百万，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"b9ed14d7dd","type":"paragraph","text":"不怕峻岭摩西天，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"72f37cdb3a","type":"paragraph","text":"不怕水深路又险，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"63aa9169cb","type":"paragraph","text":"不怕烈火在眼前。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"de479f2908","type":"paragraph","text":"纯金不怕烈火炼，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"5152275aef","type":"paragraph","text":"男儿志气似钢坚。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"3ba16686d2","type":"paragraph","text":"为真理愿做屈死鬼，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"9fc23f292e","type":"paragraph","text":"决不献媚在眼前；","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"9c9a53e558","type":"paragraph","text":"望个个敢讲心里话，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"6439ed533e","type":"paragraph","text":"实事求是往外搬。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"0169f32389","type":"paragraph","text":"过关是把将来斩，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"},{"id":"a39f1df5b9","type":"paragraph","text":"血染刀刃谢苍天。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47"}],"page":{"id":"3c5f01ef91","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e436465a47","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}